{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十四回\"华夷之战\"讲述恒河三佛追杀辛捷至海外，平凡上人带辛捷逃往小戢岛。平凡上人先以铁锚击毁大船帆桅，随后引恒河三佛进入归元古阵困住他们。他去找慧大师联手，慧大师起初不愿出手，平凡上人以激将法相激，最终两人一笑泯恩仇，联手对敌。辛捷奉命前往无极岛请无恨生相助，却因张菁失踪之事遭无恨生怒斥。无恨生因爱女十天前独自去中原寻辛捷未归，迁怒于辛捷。辛捷施展大衍十式和诘摩步法证明身份，最终以激将法和打赌之计成功说服无恨生前往小戢岛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "那几个天竺老鬼是想要你小命，我老人家不依，但我一个人却不是他们的对手，为今只有一条路好走——",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "到小戢岛去！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "正是，咱们快赶！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "只是，只是——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "只是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "只是怕那慧大师不肯——",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我好歹要激她出手——我们一到小戢岛，待我上了岸，你立刻驾船到无极岛去找那无恨生，那'恒河三佛'武功强极了，只怕我与慧大师两人抵不住。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "接招——",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "披发头陀",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "有话好好说，怎么动手就动手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "喂，有本领的走出阵来——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_fo",
      "speaker_name": "二佛",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "我们还以为这阵有什么古怪，老实说，这样一个阵，我们还不放它在眼内哩——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "好大的口气，你倒试试看。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "老尼婆，快来，来得正好——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "臭和尚又到这里吵闹作甚？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "平日你老尼婆深居简出，不问世事，今日你却非出头不可——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "不想小戢岛主竟是怕事的人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "谁说我怕事了？这倒要追究追究！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "人家逼到咱们'世外三仙'头上，你仍然不敢出手——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "你道我平凡上人是打不过人家才来请你臭尼姑？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "你既打得过何不一人去抵敌？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "以刚才他们三人推石笋的功力，你能以一敌三？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "敌不过又怎么样，老尼婆不出手，我自去找无恨生去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "且慢——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "臭和尚，你以前逗怒贫尼和贫尼打闹的事，咱们以后一概不记——",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "老尼婆困我十年，咱们这笔账一笔勾销——",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lu_e",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "喂，你们以为我们出不了这阵儿？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_jin_lu_e",
      "text": "是又怎么样？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_fo",
      "speaker_name": "二佛",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "我们把你这石头尽数推翻——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "你倒试试看。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "上来吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "咱们就在这石笋上决胜负吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈辛捷，拜见无恨生前辈，并有急事相求——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好小子，你竟到岛上来了——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "张菁呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你——你——哼哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "张菁，你是说令爱？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "她不在岛上吗——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "她，她在十天前吵着要去找你，嘿，一去不返——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "晚辈这几天流浪在海外，她去什么地方找我——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "她说是到中原去了，唉，菁儿年幼无知——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "这个晚辈也曾想到，只是晚辈现在有紧急之事在身，等此事一了，立刻踏遍神州，找回令爱——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好小子，我这就把你赶出岛去，我限你在数三下内，远远滚离此岛，永远不要见我——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "一——二－－",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "且慢！我若不是有急事相求，根本也不会踏上这岛半步，只是，只是事关天下武林——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "三——",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好小子，你是不把我放在眼内了，看我无恨生把你这不知好歹的小子赶下岛去——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好小于，你不动手？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "论功夫，晚辈怎能及得上岛主之万一呢？不过，岛主若是挟技而凌人，说不得，辛某我倒要冲撞——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好小子，有志气，你要冲撞我无恨生，还得去再苦练十年二十载——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "我倒认为不必如此之久——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "那你便试一试——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "岛主且慢——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "岛主暂请息怒，晚辈来此乃是奉平凡上人之命来请岛主前往小戢岛，有要事相商，慧大师也——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "什么平凡上人，慧大师，世外三仙的名号是你乱叫的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "小子花言巧语骗得那两个老糊涂，却骗不得我——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "唉，不料世外三仙虚得浪名——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "我说有一人武功远胜于你——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你说是谁？在什么地方？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "告诉你也不济事，你反正不敢去——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你说，你说他在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
